flowchart TD
    Q["`Research question (formed before looking at data!)`"] --> H0["Null hypothesis H₀ Default: no effect / no difference H₀: μ₁ = μ₂  or  β = 0"]
    Q --> H1["Alternative hypothesis H₁ What you want to detect Two-sided: μ₁ ≠ μ₂ One-sided: μ₁ > μ₂  or  μ₁ < μ₂"]

    subgraph ERRORS["Decision outcomes"]
        OK1["Reject H₀, H₀ false → Correct decision"]
        OK2["Fail to reject H₀, H₀ true → Correct decision"]
        T1["`Reject H₀, H₀ true → Type I error (α, false positive)`"]
        T2["`Fail to reject H₀, H₀ false → Type II error (β, false negative)`"]
    end

    H0 & H1 --> ERRORS
